<TEXT>
<P>
 Residents in Culver City and nearby areas will have an opportunity next week 
to meet the seven candidates vying for the vacant seat on the Culver Municipal 
Court bench. 
</P>
<P>
 Residents in the Culver Judicial District, which includes Marina del Rey, 
Ladera Heights, View Park, Windsor Hills and Culver City, on June 7 will elect 
a successor to Judge Harold Cherness, who announced his retirement after 19 
years.Cherness will serve until the end of the year. 
</P>
<P>
