 They have been invited to the Culver City Chamber of Commerce's monthly 
luncheon May 6 at noon at the Red Lion Hotel in Culver City. Admission for 
chamber members is $15 with reservations and $18 at the door. General admission 
is $20. Reservations: (310) 287-3850. 
</P>
<P>
 The League of Women Voters will hold a candidates forum May 18 at 7 p.m. at 
the Veterans Memorial Auditorium in Culver City. Information: (310) 559-7177. 
