decisions with a 16.71 ERA in seven appearances.He gave up 13 runs and 13 hits 
in seven innings. 
</P>
<P>
 Horsman, a left-hander, was 1-0 with a 2.57 ERA in seven games at Tacoma in 
the Pacific Coast League. 
</P>
<P>
 Righetti, who signed with Oakland as a free agent, is eighth on the career 
