</P>
<P>
 The Fullerton Friends of Music will present a "Four Hands and Four Voices" 
program, which includes Schumann's rarely performed "Spanische Liebeslieder" 
for four vocalists and two pianists Sunday, May 1, at 3:30 p.m. at Sunny Hills 
High School. Free admission. (714) 525-5836. 
</P>
