<HEADLINE>
<P>
COMMUNITY NEWS: ALHAMBRA; SENIOR RIDE PROGRAM EXTENDED TO JUNE 30 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 The city of Alhambra's Senior Ride program, which provides local transit 
service for residents 60 years or older and for disabled residents of any age, 
has been extended through June 30. 
</P>
<P>
 New patrons who want to register for the free program need to complete a form 
to get a ridership card. 
</P>
<P>
 Senior Ride operates Monday through Friday, 8 a.m. to 5 p.m.; Saturday 8 a.m. 
to 4:30 p.m., and Sunday 8 a.m. to 2 p.m. Information: (818) 570-5088. 
</P>
</TEXT>
