<LENGTH>
<P>
38 words 
</P>
</LENGTH>
<HEADLINE>
<P>
CYPRESS' MOLONEY PICKS ARIZONA STATE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Kerry Moloney, who plays first base for Cypress College, signed a letter of 
intent to play softball at Arizona State. Moloney, who attended Hacienda 
Heights Wilson High, has a batting average of .369 and 31 RBIs this season. 
</P>
