BRIEFCASE: SMALL BUSINESS; LOCAL SUCCESS STORIES WILL BE CELEBRATED AT LUNCHEON 
TODAY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
Compiled by Susan Christian, Times staff writer 
</P>
