<HEADLINE>
<P>
HOT TICKET 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 The St. Joseph Ballet is no ordinary dance company: A troupe of kids from 
inner-city Santa Ana, it has to do with self-discovery, growth, change and 
dignity at least as much as it has to do with pointe and balance. Its latest 
program bows tonight at the Irvine Barclay Theatre. 
</P>
